WEBVTT

00:00.835 --> 00:01.966
- After we received your sample,

00:02.003 --> 00:03.702
Our lab conducted an in-depth
analysis of the drug

00:03.837 --> 00:04.903
That you're calling
"purple rain."

00:04.939 --> 00:07.039
- So we're likely looking
for someone

00:07.108 --> 00:08.907
