knowledge.

00:08.976 --> 00:10.976
- I imagine at the very least
they have a master's degree,

00:10.978 --> 00:12.644
But probably a phd.

00:12.713 --> 00:14.880
- I first heard about purple
rain at a house party in guelph.

00:14.949 --> 00:16.114
- Michel owens?

00:16.150 --> 00:18.450
- He's got a phd in chemistry,
has access to the lab.

00:18.585 --> 00:19.584
Guelph tech.

00:19.620 --> 00:20.819
- Okay, here's
what I'm thinking.

00:20.888 --> 00:22.388
We take a road trip out
to guelph,

00:22.523 --> 00:23.655
Bump the guy,
see what we find.

00:23.657 --> 00:25.057
Yeah, I'm looking for
michel owens,

00:25.126 --> 00:26.958
The lab manager for
the chemistry department?

00:26.994 --> 00:29.661
- The last time he signed
into the lab was two nights ago
at midnight.

00:29.730 --> 00:32.664
- I'm not making drugs.
I'm not selling drugs.

00:33.868 --> 00:35.968
Have you talked to Tuesday?
- Who's Tuesday?

00:36.103 --> 00:38.303
- The janitor I just had fired
after I caught them

00:38.439 --> 00:40.873
After hours working late
cooking shit up in my lab

00:40.875 --> 00:42.474
And lying about it.

00:42.609 --> 00:44.009
- Did krish put you up
to all this?

00:44.078 --> 00:46.878
- I didn't make purple rain
with the intention of dealing.

00:46.914 --> 00:49.081
I was just trying
to help people.

00:49.150 --> 00:51.617
- Were you trying to help the
people who overdosed and died?

00:51.752 --> 00:55.354
Selfish. That's what my mother
told me every night of my life.

00:55.356 --> 00:58.891
Well, the nights that she was
there, which was barely ever.

00:58.893 --> 01:01.960
- Jenn can be a bit possessive.
- She doesn't want to meet me?

01:02.029 --> 01:03.161
- She...

01:04.965 --> 01:06.765
...Doesn't want to meet you.
I'm sorry.

01:09.937 --> 01:11.402
- Sam, you're home?

01:12.940 --> 01:14.106
Ro!

01:21.582 --> 01:24.249
- Keep your eye on the gps,
I need to turn around at 2.5,

01:24.384 --> 01:26.318
I cannot be late for work today.
- Me neither.

01:26.387 --> 01:28.320
Rumour is goldstein
is retiring next month,

01:28.455 --> 01:30.122
Means they'll be looking for
a new partner.

01:30.257 --> 01:32.124
This time, I'm not gonna
let it get away.

01:32.259 --> 01:34.058
- Nice. Yes!
(chuckling)

01:35.229 --> 01:37.062
- I was sensitivity-trained
twice a week, check.

01:37.064 --> 01:38.997
Gone to every conference,
check.

01:39.033 --> 01:40.932
Taken every file
they've offered, check.

01:41.001 --> 01:43.535
Been mentoring this hot,
young junior, check.

01:43.604 --> 01:46.104
- Uh...
- Okay, 2.5, let's turn around.

01:47.141 --> 01:49.141
- Okay, so who's this hot
young junior?

01:49.143 --> 01:50.709
- Jay burden, new hire.

01:50.844 --> 01:53.078
Clerked at the supreme court,
"whatevs".

01:53.147 --> 01:55.747
- Smart or entitled?
- She's pretty smart, actually.

01:55.783 --> 01:58.417
- Oh, right. Cool.
Jay's a she, that's nice.

01:58.419 --> 01:59.785
- Yeah, she is.

01:59.920 --> 02:02.821
Jay-na. She goes by jay.
Well, some people call her jay.

02:02.956 --> 02:04.156
