Here's a key.

03:01.982 --> 03:03.348
- Thank you.
- Nice to see you.

03:03.483 --> 03:05.550
- I am too, but I feel bad,

03:05.553 --> 03:07.019
I'm going to work and
you're just getting here.

03:07.154 --> 03:08.386
- We can hang out later.

03:09.156 --> 03:12.090
(groaning)
- okay.

03:14.328 --> 03:16.161
