on his back.

05:49.850 --> 05:51.916
We don't know who
krish's connections are,
it could be anyone.

05:51.952 --> 05:54.352
- I am aware, which is why
we need to convince jake mardy

05:54.355 --> 05:55.920
To testify for the crown.

05:55.989 --> 05:57.989
- He won't come out publicly
as a snitch.

05:57.991 --> 06:00.725
- Then I won't be able
to go upstairs and convince
them to sign off

06:00.794 --> 06:03.261
On the costly expense of putting
him in witness protection.

06:03.397 --> 06:04.663
He'll be on his own.

06:04.798 --> 06:06.565
- How'd they find out
he's our ci?

06:06.567 --> 06:08.767
- I don't know,
but Tuesday's lawyer

06:08.769 --> 06:11.136
Is with goldstein, jacob,
field and wells.

06:11.271 --> 06:12.670
- That's steve's firm.

06:13.674 --> 06:14.539
Oh...

06:17.044 --> 06:19.611
- Nathan, naz,
I need you to find jake mardy.

06:19.746 --> 06:22.414
Convince him to testify.
And if he agrees,

06:22.416 --> 06:24.216
We'll get him into
a safe house right away.

06:31.658 --> 06:33.124
(sighs)

06:38.331 --> 06:40.832
- Come on, guys. You know better
than to show up here.

06:40.901 --> 06:42.434
- Things have taken a turn.

06:42.569 --> 06:44.102
- Oh, of course they have.
What's up?

06:44.104 --> 06:46.170
- Somehow, the defence has
found out you've been

06:46.206 --> 06:47.371
Informing for the police.

06:47.408 --> 06:48.773
