anymore anyway, right?

07:58.245 --> 08:01.446
Think of this as an opportunity.
A fresh start.

08:02.683 --> 08:04.783
- What about my girlfriend?
What about yolanda?

08:04.785 --> 08:07.118
- You're still talking to her?
Really?

08:07.120 --> 08:09.654
