of hours and, um...

08:18.866 --> 08:20.999
Yeah. I'll get back to you,
okay? We'll figure it out.

08:21.935 --> 08:22.934
Yeah.

08:22.936 --> 08:24.135
Yeah. We'll figure it out.

08:24.137 --> 08:25.470
- Jake--
- you gotta trust me, okay?

08:25.605 --> 08:26.871
I'll call you later.

08:26.874 --> 08:28.873
